  "title": "Customer Service Officer",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma in relevant discipline.</li>\n  <li>Minimum 1- 2 years of relevant experience.</li>\n  <li>Resourceful individual and a good team player.</li>\n  <li>Positive and willing to learn, able to work independently with minimum supervision.</li>\n  <li>Effectively bilingual in English and Mandarin.</li>\n  <li>Able to start work immediately or within short notice.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Job Specifications</strong>:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Support Marketing and Sales teams in all marketing and customer support activities.</li>\n  <li>In charge of order processing from order entry until shipment.</li>\n  <li>Liaise with internal and external stakeholders to ensure on time delivery.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and check all shipping documents to ensure that they are complete and comply with import and export regulations. </li>\n  <li>Attend to queries relating to shipping documents.</li>\n  <li>Assist in developing, maintaining, enhancing existing customer relationship and handle customers' complaints.</li>\n</ul>",
